	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Maybe the PowerPak doesn't take LoROM/HiROM into account when applying ROM codes? That would break GG support for many more games than MMX, so maybe that's not the case..  Should be relatively easy to find out if it is though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


