		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The fact that the game is accessing ROM through one of the mirrors shouldn't matter. But the fact that your codes refer to these mirrors can matter depending on how/when the PowerPak applies the codes.
<br />
<br />Try using 3CAA-6DB3 &amp; 3CAA-6D23 instead.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


